{
  "stem": "1965.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This man gave him sanctuary, gave him a name to carry, as long as he stayed in his house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because my father said, I want to go to Paris.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They couldn't speak Eng-- neither one could speak each other's language.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But yet, it communicated out that my father wanted to go to Paris.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the mayor says, you cannot go to Paris.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You will be shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "By the time you come there, you'll be shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so he gave him that sanctuary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my father's name during the stay he was there, between '43 and '45, his name was known as Jean Pierre.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He had to play the role of a deaf, dumb.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And while he worked in the fields, and in the barn, and slept in the barn of this mayor and chief marquee of this region, one day while he was in the barn, Rommel came for a visit.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And Rommel stood right in front of my father and did not know that he was an escaped Jew from a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my father survived this because of the generosity of this beautiful human being.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Again, a miracle.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And when my father returned after the war to Antwerp, these two men each year corresponded with each other until the immigration to the United States.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have absolutely no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if I had paid more attention as a child when my father was getting the correspondence from this person, who was, at that time, the mayor, and I don't know how long he was mayor.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if I had taken the notes down-- I regret this.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
